column5: I tried to get this fellows attention but he did not hear me. You were in a red Jeep, pulling a tinner with the name, "the dirty Oar". I noticed that the right side tire and wheel were at a 10 degree tilt of of vertical. If you see this I would suggest that you check your bearings on the trailer.
Maybe it's a popular name, cuz I've seen a boat with name before.  Just remember who...
